movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Great movie
review: I just started watching all the movies over again since Galaxy's Edge opened and this one is amazing (and definitely not just for kids).

title: Wanted more!!
review: My only objection is I wish they had played his entire 2nd studio album, Tumbleweed Connection album, Madman Across the Water album and Honky Chateau album and then I would have been REALLY happy! Great movie anyway though!

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode IX - The Rise of Skywalker
title: Amazing
review: I loved it - sad to see all the trolls bashing another great Star Wars movie (and I saw the first movie when it was released in theaters when I was a teenager, so I'm not a new fan although I am female).
